caller_intent: The caller is seeking commercial insurance for a box truck rented from Ryder and is willing to provide documentation via email to facilitate the process.
resolution_steps: Agent Stacy confirms the caller's need for commercial insurance related to a Ryder-rented box truck.
Caller agrees to email documentation if provided with an email address.
Agent requests the caller's email address, which the caller spells out phonetically (propnewhow@yahoo.com).
Agent confirms the email address and assures the caller a commercial agent will follow up.
summary: A caller inquires about commercial insurance for a Ryder-rented box truck. The agent collects the caller's email address (propnewhow@yahoo.com) and schedules a follow-up with a commercial agent. The call concludes with confirmation of next steps and contact information.
